    "pages": [
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "minecraft:white_bed",
            "text": "$(li)Beds are blocks that allows you to sleep at night, passing time faster than normal until the sun rises again.$(br)$(li)You only have to right click on the bed during the night to activate this event.",  
            "link_recipe": "true"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "$(li)By default, when you die, you respawn in the place where you adventure begins.$(br)$(li)If you right click on a bed, the spawnpoint will change to that bed.$(br)$(li)If that bed is destroyed you will lose the spawnpoint.$(br)$(li)As other blocks, Beds can be dyed too.$(br)$(li)$(l:patchouli:villagers/shepherd)Shepherds$(/l) will exchange your $(l:patchouli:miscellaneous/vanilla/emerald)Emeralds$(/l) by Beds."
        },
